summary: A really tiny hunting shack in a cave.
descriptionHtml:
A really tiny hunting shack in a cave near dawnstar. If you consider nord females with no clothes on (They have the bra and underwear) inappropriate then don\'t download. It\'s still a tiny bit glitchy (With the females having a male voice and what not) but it will be updated soon. I just wanted to get a version up and running first.

Dedicated to my friend Meagan.
Happy birthday!!
author: Dextronium
